				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tineras wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">My question is, where do the 256 bytes come from?</div>
<br />From (N * $100) to (N * $100 + $FF). The number written to $4014 specifies which page (256-byte chunk) from CPU memory gets copied to OAM. If you write 2, $0200-$02FF will be copied.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

